Package com.tangosol.coherence.dsltools.precedence

Class InfixRightOPToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tangosol.coherence.dsltools.precedence.OPToken
      • com.tangosol.coherence.dsltools.precedence.InfixRightOPToken
  • public class InfixRightOPToken
extends OPToken
    InfixRightOPToken is used to implement infix operators that like to bind to the right which is typical of exponentiation rules.
    Author:
    djl 2009.03.14
